page_title: 'How to use Azure OpenAI Assistants function calling'
page_description: Learn how to use Assistants function calling
chunk_content: Reading the functionsWhen you initiate a Run with a user Message that triggers the function, the Run will enter a pending status. After it processes, the run will enter a requires_action state that you can verify by retrieving the Run.```json{  "id": "run_abc123",  "object": "thread.run",  "assistant_id": "asst_abc123",  "thread_id": "thread_abc123",  "status": "requires_action",  "required_action": {    "type": "submit_tool_outputs",    "submit_tool_outputs": {      "tool_calls": [        {          "id": "call_abc123",          "type": "function",          "function": {            "name": "getCurrentWeather",            "arguments": "{\"location\":\"San Francisco\"}"          }        },        {          "id": "call_abc456",          "type": "function",          "function": {            "name": "getNickname",            "arguments": "{\"location\":\"Los Angeles\"}"          }        }      ]    }  },...```
